sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant R as Workflow Runtime
    participant J as Scheduled Jobs Store
    participant S as Internal Scheduler
    participant G as Guardrails (TTL / Retry / Timeout)

    R ->> J: upsert next_wakeup_at when status = WAITING

    loop workflow-tick
        S ->> J: fetch due jobs
        alt job not yet due
            S ->> S: continue polling
        else job due
            S ->> R: lock run and resume evaluation
            R ->> G: check retry budget + timeout + ttl
            alt budget exhausted
                G -->> R: fail
                R -->> J: terminal update: FAILED or stale
            else budget valid
                G -->> R: continue
                alt still WAITING
                    R -->> J: write new next_wakeup_at
                else state advanced
                    R -->> J: status + events update
                end
            end
        end
    end
